(94, 1, '2020-06-15 03:53:22', '2020-06-15 03:53:22', '<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"has-text-align-center\">What can&nbsp;<strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-accent-color\">*</span></strong>&nbsp;mean besides equal contribution?</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The images link you to the detailed webpages, if possible. A compact list can be found at my <a href=\"https://scholar.google.ca/citations?hl=en&amp;user=TZh189YAAAAJ\">Google Scholar</a>. The works I am proud of are marked <span class=\"has-inline-color has-accent-color\">RED</span>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Publications', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '90-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-15 03:53:22', '2020-06-15 03:53:22', '', 90, 'http://localhost/homepage/2020/06/15/90-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
