 <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"https://mila.quebec/yoshua-bengio/\">Yoshua Bengio</a>, at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cs.mcgill.ca/\">School of Computer Science</a>&nbsp;of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/\">McGill University</a>. In 2020, I graduated as a MSc., advised by <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~chang/\">Xiao-Wen Chang</a>, with CGPA 4.0/4.0.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":244,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/logo-frq-couleur-1/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":20,\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"full\",\"imageFill\":false} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:20% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/logo-frq-couleur-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">I am a recipient of the <a href=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/en/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/en/\">FRQ (Nature and Technologies)</a> funds. My file was ranked<strong> <span class=\"has-inline-color has-accent-color\">1st </span></strong>place among all 2020 contenders. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":74,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/dlut_logo/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":15,\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 15%\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http:/