"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"https://mila.quebec/yoshua-bengio/\">Yoshua Bengio</a>, at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cs.mcgill.ca/\">School of Computer Science</a>&nbsp;of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/\">McGill University</a>. In 2020, I graduated as a MSc., advised by <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~chang/\">Xiao-Wen Chang</a>, with CGPA 4.0/4.0.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":358,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/haiper/\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":15,\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"full\",\"imageFill\":false} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:15% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/haiperai/\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Haiper.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-358 size-full\"/></a></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">I am a research scientist (part-time) at <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/haiperai/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/haiperai/\">Haiper LTD</a>, mentored by <a href=\"https://ziyuw.github.io/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://ziyuw.github.io/\">Ziyu Wang</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/yishumiao\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://sites.google.com/view/yishumiao\">Yishu Miao</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":359,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/ms/\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":15,\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 15%\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/lab/microsoft-research-montreal/\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/MS.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-359 size-full\"/></a></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">I am a research intern at <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/lab/microsoft-research-montreal/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/lab/microsoft-research-montreal/\">Microsoft Research (Montreal)</a>, mentored by <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/havansei/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/havansei/\">Harm van Seijen</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":244,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/logo-frq-couleur-1/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":20,\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"full\",\"imageFill\":false} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:20% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/logo-frq-couleur-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">I was the <strong>1st </strong>place recipient of the <a href=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/en/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/en/\">FRQ (Nature and Technologies)</a> funds (2020).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":74,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/dlut_logo/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":15,\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 15%\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/DLUT_logo.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-74 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">I was an undergrad at <a href=\"https://en.dlut.edu.cn/\">Dalian University of Technology</a>, with major in Computer Science and Technology, and minor in Creative Practices (robotics). I received the Outstanding Student Researcher Award of class 2018 and graduated with 90+ percentage.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":238,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/saxophone-brass-blow-jazz-instrument-512/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":15,\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:15% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/saxophone-brass-blow-jazz-instrument-512.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-238 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">I had been studying saxophone performance, before switching to science.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --