n-us/research/lab/microsoft-research-montreal/\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/MS.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-359 size-full\"/></a></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"25px\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:25px\">I am also a research intern at <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/lab/microsoft-research-montreal/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/lab/microsoft-research-montreal/\">Microsoft Research</a>, mentored by <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/havansei/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/havansei/\">Harm van Seijen</a>, <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/retachet/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/retachet/\">Remi Tachet</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/rolaroch/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/rolaroch/\">Romain Laroche</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":244,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/logo-frq-couleur-1/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":20,\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"full\",\"imageFill\":false} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:20% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/logo-frq-couleur-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"25px\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:25px\">I was honored to be <strong>1st </strong>place recipient of the 2020 <a href=\"https:/