(413, 1, '2022-10-05 09:00:49', '2022-10-05 13:00:49', '<!-- wp:block {\"ref\":197} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hey, this is Harry :) Welcome to my page!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>My Present</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am a Ph.D. student advised by <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a> and <a href=\"https://mila.quebec/yoshua-bengio/\">Yoshua Bengio</a>, at <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/\">McGill University</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am an OG researcher at <a href=\"https://mila.quebec/en/\">Mila</a> (Quebec AI Institute), interested in the learning aspects of AI x human brain.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am also a research intern at <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/lab/microsoft-research-montreal/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/lab/microsoft-research-montreal/\">Microsoft Research</a>, mentored by <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/havansei/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/havansei/\">Harm van Seijen</a>, <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/retachet/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/retachet/\">Remi Tachet</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/rolaroch/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/rolaroch/\">Romain Laroche</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am a research scientist at <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/haiperai/\">Haiper</a>, working closely with <a href=\"https://ziyuw.github.io/\">Ziyu Wang</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/yishumiao\">Yishu Miao</a>. We are a startup that turns your iPhones into 3D scanners, uploading objects into the meta-verse.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Research Interest</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Reinforcement Learning (theory and practice), Deep Learning</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Computational perspectives of consciousness</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Novel View Synthesis</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>News</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[2021] Conscious planning paper received media coverage from ...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[2021] I was honored to be <strong>1st </strong>place recipient of the 2020 <a href=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/en/\">FRQ (Nature and Technologies)</a> PhD excellence fellowship funds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[2018] I received B.Eng from <a href=\"https://en.dlut.edu.cn/\">Dalian University of Technology</a>, with the honor of Outstanding Student Researcher of class 2018.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>More About Me</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I love reading history and psychology. Understanding humanity is one of my greatest passion.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have a cute orange cat. His name is Sir!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Music is a huge part of my life. I am right now slowly learning the violin. I studied music performance (wind instruments) when I was young, before pursuing my dream as a scientist :)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My Instagram handle is @pwnerharry, where I post things about my life.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!--