ao</a>. We are a startup that turns your iPhones into 3D scanners, uploading objects into the meta-verse.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Research Interest</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Reinforcement Learning (theory and practice), Deep Learning</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Computational perspectives of consciousness</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Novel View Synthesis</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>News</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[2021] Conscious planning paper received media coverage from ...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[2021] I was honored to be <strong>1st </strong>place recipient of the 2020 <a href=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/en/\">FRQ (Nature and Technologies)</a> PhD excellence fellowship funds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[2018] I received B.Eng from <a href=\"https://en.dlut.edu.cn/\">Dalian University of Technology</a>, with the honor of Outstanding Student Researcher of class 2018.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>More About Me</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I love reading history and psychology. Understanding humanity is one of my greatest passion.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have a cute orange cat. His name is Sir!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Music is a huge part of my life. I am right now slowly learning the violin. I studied music performance (wind instruments) when I was young, before pursuing my dream as a scientist :)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My Instagram handle is @pwnerharry, 