 href=\"https://ziyuw.github.io/\">Ziyu Wang</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/yishumiao\">Yishu Miao</a>. We are a startup that turns your iPhones into 3D scanners, uploading real-world objects into the meta-verse.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Research Interest</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Reinforcement Learning (theory and practice), Deep Learning</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Computational perspectives of consciousness, Planning, Neuro-Inspired AI</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Novel View Synthesis</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>News</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[2021] Conscious planning paper received media coverage from <a href=\"https://medium.com/syncedreview/yoshua-bengio-team-designs-consciousness-inspired-planning-agent-for-model-based-rl-501b4d7e80f5\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://medium.com/syncedreview/yoshua-bengio-team-designs-consciousness-inspired-planning-agent-for-model-based-rl-501b4d7e80f5\">Synced Review</a>,  <a href=\"https://mila.quebec/en/article/a-consciousness-inspired-planning-agent-for-model-based-reinforcement-learning/\">The Mila Blog</a> (available in English &amp; French), <a href=\"https://www.marktechpost.com/2021/06/18/ai-researchers-including-yoshua-bengio-introduce-a-consciousness-inspired-planning-agent-for-model-based-reinforcement-learning/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.marktechpost.com/2021/06/18/ai-researchers-including-yoshua-bengio-introduce-a-consciousness-inspired-planning-agent-for-model-based-reinforcement-learning/\">MarkTechPost</a>, etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[2021] I was honored to be <strong>1st </strong>place recipient of the 2020 <a href=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/en/\">FRQ (Nature and Technologies)</a> PhD excellence fellowship funds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[2020] I graduated my M.S. from <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/\">McGill University</a> with CGPA 4.0/4.0, advised by <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a> and <a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~chang/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~chang/\">Xiao-Wen Chang</a>. Check out <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2006.08906\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2006.08906\">my thesis</a> on using meta-learning to accelerate temporal difference learning.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[2018] I received my B.Eng from <a href=\"https://en.dlut.edu.cn/\">Dalian University of Technology</a> with 90%+ CGPA, elected with the honor of Outstanding Student Researcher of class 2018. My thesis was on transfer learning in Deep Reinforcement Learning (DRL). The original thesis was in Mandarin and not open to public however you could check <a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/8852019\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/8852019\">the conference version here</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>More About Me</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I love reading history and psychology. Understanding humanity is one of my greatest passion.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have a cute orange cat. His name is Sir!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am try-lingual (not counting the programming languages), learning French!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Music is a huge part of my life. I am right now slowly learning the violin. I studied music performance (wind instruments) when I was young, before pursuing my dream as a scientist :)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My Instagram handle is <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/pwnerharry/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.instagram.com/pwnerharry/\">@pwnerharry</a>, where I post things about my life.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"12px\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Site Last Updated: 05 Oct 2022</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Understanding Intelligence', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-10-05 09:35:21', '2022-10-05 13:35:21', '', 36, 'http://localhost/homepage/?p=438', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
